## ?? Data Safety

- **Confirmation Dialogs**: Prevents accidental deletion
- **Export Backup**: Easy to create CSV backups
- **Refresh Option**: Reload if changes are made elsewhere
- **Error Handling**: User-friendly error messages
- **No Auto-Delete**: Must explicitly select and confirm

