## ?? What's Different from Main Form

| Feature | Main Form | Show Table Form |
|---------|-----------|-----------------|
| **Purpose** | Data Entry | Data Viewing |
| **Layout** | Single record | All records |
| **Edit** | Direct fields | Grid cells |
| **Navigation** | Next/Previous | Scroll/Sort |
| **Search** | No | Yes |
| **Delete** | No | Yes |
| **Export** | No | Yes |
| **View Count** | Current | All visible |

